-- TAKE A LOOK-BES changes put Portuguese banks in spotlight
-- 
-- Tue Jun 24, 2014 06:07AM EDT
-- None



LONDON, June 24 (Reuters) - A month after Portugal emerged from an international bailout, changes loom in its banking sector including at Banco Espirito Santo <BES.LS> where the chief executive has agreed to step down.

